{
  "stem": "11671.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the very first day-- he's with his American uniform-- the very first day he came to visit us, we were, you know, very-- everybody-- he was so special.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, he was an American soldier.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we were dancing, and we were singing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when-- the famous dance and song where the young people used to do in Europe is where it talks about how the train is traveling through the mountains, and the rocks.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, of all the girls I pick you to dance with.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then the girl goes-- in the same song-- and then says, of all the boys I pick you to dance.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Can you sing it for us, Penina?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I can still sing it because I heard it so many times here, too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It goes-- my beautiful voice, but it goes like-- [NON-ENGLISH SINGING] And then again, [NON-ENGLISH] means 'the boy' in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SINGING]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, 'I love you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I want to pick you.' It's not 'pick you,' but, 'I love you.' So when they danced, and then the girl picked Harold.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then when Harold's turn to pick-- came to pick a girl, he motioned, he went over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he put his hand out, and he asked me to come.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So at first, I didn't want to come dance with him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then finally, I did come.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After the third try, I did come to dance with him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I came down to dance with him, they all started to applaud and say, ah-ha, ah-ha, hey, you la la, you like.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They're meaning, OK, this is the boy that met the girl, that really likes the girl.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we danced.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that was the very first time when we met.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
